linkedGraph

Class PathList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • linkedGraph.PathList<T>

  • public class PathList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic List class that is customized for the Graph data structure. Typical methods for Lists are omitted if unused. This class can be used to hold the possible paths between 2 vertices, all possible paths in the adjacency list, and a list of each vertex's adjacent vertices.
    Author:
    wchan
